sourcesContent: {{ coffee.name }} Place: {{ coffee.place }} create import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { DataService } from '../data.service'; import { Coffee } from '../logic/Coffee'; @Component({ selector: 'app-list', templateUrl: './list.component.html', styleUrls: ['./list.component.css'] }) export class ListComponent { coffeeList!: [Coffee]; constructor(private data: DataService){ } ngOnInit(){ this.data.getList((list: [Coffee]) => { this.coffeeList = list; }) } }
